Presto is a Hypermedia driven generic editing framework. It consists of an HTTP interface for retrieving information and editing that information. The APIs are fully usable, but still in development and will change.

==Features==
  * Hypermedia driven generic editing.
  * Multiple data providers available (CouchDB and Ontopia).
  * JSON over HTTP using Hypermedia implemented in Java/JAX-RS.

